quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  17,23,"N’umuvyeyi wawe yaciye urubanza rwuko mutazosenga uwariwe wese atari Imana yonyene gusa, hamwe nukugirira ineza ntangere abavyeyi bose uko ari babiri, hanyuma umwe muribo ageze muzabukuru muri kumwe nabo, canke bose uko ari babiri, rero ntubabwire ijambo rivuga riti:- Ah! kandi ntuba kankamire, kandi ubavugishe imvugo y’urupfasoni rwiza"
  17,24,"Kandi ubamanurire ibaba ry’ubu gamburutsi hamwe n’ikigongwe hanyuma uvuga uti:- Muremyi wanje, nubahezagire nkuko bandeze nkiri uruhinja"
  17,25,"Umuremyi wanyu niwe afise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mumishaha yanyu, nimwaba muri mubantu beranda kuriyo n’uwuzoba girira ikigongwe kubantu bagaruka muruhongore rwiwe"
  17,26,"Kandi umuhe incuti yawe ibikenewe kuriwe, n’umworo hamwe n’uwononekewe ari murugendo, kandi ntusesagure amatungo yawe nabi nabi"
  17,27,"Mu vy’ukuri abakoresha amatungo yabo nabi nabi abo nibo bagenzi b’ama Shetani, na Shetani niyo nyene guhakana Umuremyi wayo"
  17,28,"Niwaba hakana mugabo urondera imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe wizera, rero nuvugane nabo amajambo yoroshe"
  17,29,"Kandi ntugire ukuboko kwawe nkukwabohewe mw’izosi ryawe, canke ntukuzingurure nabi nabi bazoca baguterako umwikomo nukurwa mubukene"
  17,30,"Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe azingururira imigisha yayo kuwo yishakiye, nukuyima uwo yishakiye mu vy’ukuri nayo kubashumvyi bayo niyo ibazi nukuba bona"